Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.25,0:02:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough, you fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.21,0:02:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A head-on clash between\Nthe Akazaya members and Kaido now begins!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.05,0:02:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you'll eventually\Nget tired from running and die!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.60,0:02:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't wait to see how many you can dodge!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.49,0:03:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"An Inherited Technique!\NUnleashing Oden's Secret Swordplay!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.41,0:03:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaido!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.63,0:03:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.73,0:03:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.07,0:03:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's cold! I feel cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.82,0:03:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Somebody, help...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.45,0:03:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.21,0:03:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This chaotic battle will end\Nwhen the samurai's hope is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.34,0:04:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can locate him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.09,0:04:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bao Huang.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.38,0:04:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can count on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.26,0:04:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you running?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.64,0:04:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you I'm Kozuki Oden!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.55,0:04:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what you're talking about!\NSo fishy! Incomprehensible!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.78,0:04:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?! Are you hurt?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.99,0:04:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.95,0:04:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Momonosuke-{\i1}kun{\i0}, are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.95,0:04:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Momonosuke-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.66,0:04:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like he is really worried about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.83,0:04:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Momonosuke-{\i1}sama{\i0}, don't be fooled.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.05,0:04:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Momonosuke-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.76,0:04:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always been waiting to see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.80,0:04:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me protect you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.35,0:04:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It does not look to me like he is lying...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.89,0:04:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who is that man?\NWhy does he care about me so much?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.98,0:05:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're there, right, Momonosuke-{\i1}kun{\i0}?!\NI'm glad that you're okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.86,0:05:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Kozuki Oden, so I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.62,0:05:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...what my son Momonosuke-{\i1}kun{\i0} smells like!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.15,0:05:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Do I smell that bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.50,0:05:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like your smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.83,0:05:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You smell very good...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.09,0:05:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you hurt, Momonosuke-{\i1}sama{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.90,0:05:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I am okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.99,0:05:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.10,0:05:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come jump into my arms!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.40,0:05:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?!\NAre you going through a rebellious phase?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.96,0:05:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}On the snowy...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.50,0:06:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...night{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.82,0:06:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The two...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.03,0:06:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...who missed each other{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.04,0:06:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But they didn't get a chance{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.87,0:06:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To see each other for so long{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.17,0:06:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Finally seeing each other{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.21,0:06:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Under the moonlight{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.38,0:07:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That excitement!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.41,0:08:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kin-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.71,0:08:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kin-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.34,0:08:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll avenge Oden-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.77,0:08:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.35,0:08:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really wanna die that badly?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.80,0:08:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kin-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.30,0:08:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.02,0:09:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fools are so annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.89,0:09:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How boring...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.77,0:09:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that's all you've got after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.69,0:09:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not even remotely close \Nto Oden's swordplay...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.57,0:09:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.62,0:10:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the samurai!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.41,0:10:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.85,0:10:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate the samurai!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.22,0:10:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.02,0:10:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am definitely going to...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.65,0:10:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...avenge Oden-{\i1}sama{\i0} today!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.86,0:10:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.15,0:10:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are only the remnants \Nof Oden's group here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.66,0:10:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What am I doing?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.82,0:10:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it'll help Oden-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.84,0:10:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.38,0:10:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to bring down Kaido!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.76,0:11:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oden-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.51,0:11:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even though I made it this far,\NI have not accomplished anything yet...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.56,0:11:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys, listen carefully!\NI'm gonna teach you how to use...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.40,0:11:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Oden Two-Sword Style!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.65,0:11:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll initiate you into my secret arts!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.66,0:11:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get to inherit Oden Two-Sword Style?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.46,0:11:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I started following him\Nwithout his permission...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.59,0:11:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did not expect I would inherit\NOden-{\i1}sama{\i0}'s secret arts as a samurai of the Land of Wano...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.93,0:11:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is a great honor!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.51,0:11:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am happy to inherit Oden-{\i1}sama{\i0}'s will!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.10,0:11:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.56,0:11:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is wrong, you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.83,0:11:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you see?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.46,0:12:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you think\Nyou alone have the right to inherit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.63,0:12:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Why"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.40,0:12:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I am definitely his best disciple!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.09,0:12:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kin-{\i1}san{\i0}, that's nonsense! If the order of\Njoining his clan matters, we joined the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.51,0:12:14.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, respect matters more than the order!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.01,0:12:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I respect Oden-{\i1}sama{\i0} the most!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.18,0:12:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm the one who'll inherit it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.63,0:12:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one else!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.78,0:12:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, if that's the case, it's gonna be me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.03,0:12:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You use {\i1}shuriken{\i0}.\NSo leave the two-sword style to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.99,0:12:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You-{\i1}gara {\i0}have a different \Nkind of sword style!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.19,0:12:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since he has such a big heart,\NI should be the one to inherit his secret arts!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.37,0:12:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why bother passing it down \Nto a small-hearted man?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.13,0:12:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I'll inherit it!\N--What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.67,0:12:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.86,0:12:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love Oden-{\i1}sama{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.70,0:12:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...more than anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.70,0:12:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You coward! Don't try to pull that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.56,0:12:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love Oden-{\i1}sama{\i0} more than anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.64,0:12:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--No, I do!\N--Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.31,0:13:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It's me!\N--I love him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.86,0:13:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--No, it must be me!\N--No, me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.26,0:13:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--So it's me!\N--Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.53,0:13:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Me!\N--No, it's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.62,0:13:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Me!\N--Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.63,0:13:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the one!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.20,0:13:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are right, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.15,0:13:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, guys! I'm gonna teach you\Nhow to use Oden Two-Sword Style!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.04,0:13:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.19,0:13:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have our own style...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.78,0:13:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.46,0:13:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.37,0:13:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It is true that\Nour strengths are nothing like Oden-{\i0}sama{\i1}'s.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.88,0:13:38.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.53,0:13:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kin-{\i1}san{\i0}, you're getting fired up\Nin your head as always...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.51,0:13:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're trying to go off by yourself again,\Naren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.36,0:13:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kin-{\i1}san{\i0} always does that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.55,0:13:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.86,0:13:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's been a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.60,0:13:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...since we fought together like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.13,0:14:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember the days we ate \NOden-{\i1}sama{\i0}'s {\i1}oden{\i0} together.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.27,0:14:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna eat fish cake with burdock...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.17,0:14:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eggs are better!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.28,0:14:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, {\i1}shirataki{\i0} noodles are the best.\NThere's no argument!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.90,0:14:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're my little brother,\Nbut you're clueless...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.12,0:14:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ganmodoki{\i0} is the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.61,0:14:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.67,0:14:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chicken wings are everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.21,0:14:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As always, no one backed down...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.22,0:14:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we are comrades\Nwho sat around a pot together!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.39,0:14:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I put too much pressure on myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.14,0:14:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's fight again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.11,0:14:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are not Oden after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.78,0:14:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were acting like great samurai\Nunder Oden's wing,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.72,0:14:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and even now, after Oden's death,\Nyou're still like kids playing samurai.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.80,0:14:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What can you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.36,0:15:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you fight us\Nand find out if we are really just playing samurai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.84,0:15:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right... Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.58,0:15:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.36,0:15:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crimson Cat Dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.20,0:15:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kappa Style!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.45,0:15:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,River of Sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.87,0:15:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.47,0:15:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Canine...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.48,0:15:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Scourge!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.64,0:15:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fallen Snow Scythes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.64,0:16:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Slicing Rounds!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.41,0:16:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.12,0:16:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Their attacks are nothing \Nlike Oden's swordplay.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.72,0:16:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How can they cut me?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.71,0:16:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaido!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.97,0:16:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.13,0:16:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.60,0:16:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ninpo: Scrolling Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.15,0:16:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My scroll will roll up anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.38,0:17:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give it back to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.30,0:17:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blast Breath!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.47,0:17:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Restoration!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.62,0:17:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.37,0:17:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Raizo, you were almost too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.64,0:17:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that made Kaido drop his guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.68,0:18:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think you can kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.39,0:18:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are merely his \Nspineless retainers...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.63,0:18:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...who only chase your lord Oden's shadow!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.20,0:18:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That is right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.78,0:18:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We have always been spineless.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.48,0:18:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna teach you\Nhow to use Oden Two-Sword Style!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.91,0:18:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.87,0:18:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have our own style...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.86,0:18:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?! It's Oden Two-Sword Style!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.51,0:18:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you wanna inherit it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.30,0:18:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Of course, we wanted to inherit it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.80,0:18:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everyone insisted they \Nwere his first disciple.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.05,0:18:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We had a serious fight\Nto decide who was his best disciple.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.76,0:18:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We all loved him too much,\Nso it looked like a fight to the death.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.98,0:18:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We admired him so much...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.98,0:18:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then why were we running, leaving him behind?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.15,0:19:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We were nothing but hoodlums\Nbefore he led us!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.41,0:19:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We knew how big his heart was.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.08,0:19:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}By believing in him,\Nwe could become stronger and stronger.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.58,0:19:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But we could not save even him!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.67,0:19:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We could not save the Land of Wano!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.34,0:19:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We have always been thinking!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.55,0:19:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If only we were stronger!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.22,0:19:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If we were strong enough to save Oden-{\i0}sama{\i1}!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.89,0:19:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If we are going to die anyway,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.19,0:19:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}let us at least die as Oden-{\i0}sama{\i1}'s samurai!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.68,0:20:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oden!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.89,0:20:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two-Sword Style!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.35,0:20:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.36,0:20:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What rubbish!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.70,0:20:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, guys! Ryuo is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.70,0:20:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.29,0:20:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We polished our sword skills\Nto save the Land of Wano today!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.30,0:20:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaido!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.40,0:21:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blast Breath!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.40,0:21:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Flame-Rend!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.55,0:22:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.51,0:22:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the samurai!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.18,0:22:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People will talk about how heroically you died\Nfor generations...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.06,0:22:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind being forgotten!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.19,0:22:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My spirit...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.69,0:22:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...will live on!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.36,0:22:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oden Two-Sword Style!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.53,0:22:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Paradise Totsuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.54,0:23:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our beloved Luffy-{\i1}senpai{\i0}\Nwho aims at becoming the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.72,0:23:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He creates havoc all over the Land of Wano\Nto take down Kaido
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.43,0:23:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who dominated the country!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.46,0:23:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, Bartolomeo, will tell you all about\Nhis numerous adventures in that territory!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.43,0:23:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!\N"Special Episode: Barto's Secret Room"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.64,0:23:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-{\i1}senpai{\i0}'s gonna become \Nthe King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.52,0:23:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.53,0:23:49.53,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,
